      • generateInstants

        public static void generateInstants(PrescriptionTiming currentTiming,
                    int rangeMin,
                    int rangeMax)
                             throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
        Generates instants for the @param currentTiming object based on the frequency and interval of the timing. It is an error if instants have already been assigned.
        Parameters:
        currentTiming - - the timing object to operate on.
        rangeMin - - the minimum number in the range (also the first instant) e.g. 8:00
        rangeMax - - the maximum number to distribute the instants across e.g. 22:00
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the timing object already has instants assigned.
